<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= title || 'Register - IT Care' %></title>
  <meta name="description" content="Daftar akun helpdesk internal IT Care">
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body class="auth-page">
  <%- include('../partials/flash') %>

  <div class="auth-shell">
    <div class="auth-grid">
      <section class="auth-side">
        <div>
          <div class="sidebar-brand-link sidebar-logo">
            <span class="brand-mark"><i class="bi bi-grid-1x2-fill"></i></span>
            <span>
              <span class="brand-name">IT<span>Care</span></span>
              <span class="brand-caption">Internal helpdesk workspace</span>
            </span>
          </div>
          <div class="auth-kicker">Registrasi Akun</div>
          <h1>Buat akun baru dengan struktur data yang siap dipakai tim.</h1>
          <p>Lengkapi identitas kerja agar tiket, assignment, dan laporan operasional tetap konsisten sejak awal.</p>
          <ul class="auth-points">
            <li><i class="bi bi-check2"></i><span>Role tetap mengikuti alur yang sudah dipakai backend</span></li>
            <li><i class="bi bi-check2"></i><span>Departemen dan nomor telepon langsung tersimpan untuk kebutuhan tiket</span></li>
            <li><i class="bi bi-check2"></i><span>Tampilan sejalan dengan dashboard SaaS internal yang lebih profesional</span></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="auth-card auth-card-wide">
        <div class="auth-header">
          <div class="sidebar-brand-link sidebar-logo">
            <span class="brand-mark logo-icon"><i class="bi bi-grid-1x2-fill"></i></span>
            <span>
              <span class="brand-name">IT<span>Care</span></span>
              <span class="brand-caption">Pendaftaran pengguna</span>
            </span>
          </div>
          <h2>Register</h2>
          <p class="auth-subtitle">Masukkan data akun kerja yang akan digunakan di sistem helpdesk.</p>
        </div>

        <form action="/register" method="POST" id="registerForm">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label class="form-label-custom" for="name">Nama Lengkap</label>
            <input type="text" name="name" id="name" class="form-control-custom" placeholder="Nama lengkap Anda" required>
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label class="form-label-custom" for="email">Email</label>
            <input type="email" name="email" id="email" class="form-control-custom" placeholder="email@company.com" required>
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label class="form-label-custom" for="regPassword">Password</label>
            <div class="input-shell">
              <input type="password" name="password" id="regPassword" class="form-control-custom" placeholder="Minimal 6 karakter" required minlength="6">
              <button type="button" class="btn-icon-app" data-password-toggle="#regPassword" aria-label="Tampilkan password">
                <i class="bi bi-eye"></i>
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="form-grid-2">
            <div class="form-group">
              <label class="form-label-custom" for="role">Role</label>
              <select name="role" id="role" class="form-control-custom">
                <option value="karyawan" selected>Karyawan</option>
                <option value="teknisi">Teknisi</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label class="form-label-custom" for="department">Departemen</label>
              <input type="text" name="department" id="department" class="form-control-custom" placeholder="Finance, HR, IT...">
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label class="form-label-custom" for="phone">Nomor Telepon</label>
            <input type="text" name="phone" id="phone" class="form-control-custom" placeholder="08xxxxxxxxxx">
          </div>

          <button type="submit" class="btn-primary-app btn-block">Daftar</button>
        </form>

        <div class="auth-link-row">
          Sudah punya akun? <a href="/login">Masuk di sini</a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/app.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
